{"about_the_game":"Drift through diverse landscapes and encounter breathtaking scenery that sparks the imagination. Whether gliding through futuristic cityscapes, navigating through enchanted forests, or conquering post-apocalyptic wastelands, every diorama presents a new challenge and a visually stunning backdrop.<br><br>Unlock the secrets hidden within each diorama, uncovering hidden paths, shortcuts, and surprises that add layers of depth to your exploration. The fail-free nature of the game allows players to focus on the thrill of the journey, experimenting with different drifting techniques and mastering the nuances of each diorama.<br><br>Whether you're a seasoned racer looking for a fresh and innovative experience or a casual player seeking a visually enchanting adventure, this game promises a one-of-a-kind journey through ever-changing landscapes that will leave you breathless and eager for the next diorama to unfold. Get ready to lose yourself in the art of drifting and embark on an unforgettable ride.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features of full release</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lots of vehicles<br></li><li>Dozens of dioramas<br></li><li>Different weather conditions<br></li><li>Radio stations</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1709323058","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529260/page.bg.jpg?t=1709323058","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529260/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1709323058","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529260/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1709323058","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Drift through diverse landscapes and encounter breathtaking scenery that sparks the imaginat